From {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|τραπέζιον||irregular quadrilateral|lit=a little table|lang=grc}} + {{term|-oid||resembling|lang=en}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{enPR|tră'pəzoid}}, {{IPA|/ˈtɹæpəzɔɪd/|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{context|geometry|lang=en}} A ([[convex]]) [[quadrilateral]] with two (non-adjacent) parallel sides.
# {{context|anatomy|lang=en}} The [[trapezoid bone]] of the [[wrist]].
# {{context|geometry|British|obsolete|lang=en}} A [[convex]] [[quadrilateral]] with no sides parallel and no equal sides.

